    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "the \"sleek and controlled\" thing is interesting. what about people who don't have naturally straight hair? like if someone has natural curls, braids, or locs, would those styles fall into the \"distracting\" or \"voluminous\" category you mentioned? how should they approach it if they want to stay authoritative?",
